text: THE QUICK BROWN FOX JUMPS OVER THE LAZY DOG.
THE CAT SAT ON THE MAT.
SHE SELLS SEASHELLS BY THE SEASHORE.
I LIKE TO EAT PIZZA ON FRIDAYS.
HE PLAYS GUITAR EVERY DAY.
THE SUN RISES IN THE EAST AND SETS IN THE WEST.
MY FAVORITE COLOR IS BLUE.
THE BOY RAN TO CATCH THE BUS.
SHE LOVES TO READ BOOKS ON RAINY DAYS.
THE BABY LAUGHED AND PLAYED WITH THE TOY.
JOHN AND JANE WENT TO THE STORE TO BUY SOME MILK.
THE TEACHER WROTE A MESSAGE ON THE WHITEBOARD.
MY DOG BARKS AT STRANGERS.
THE BUTTERFLY FLEW FROM FLOWER TO FLOWER.
THE TRAIN ARRIVED AT THE STATION ON TIME.
THE CHILDREN PLAYED IN THE PARK ON A SUNNY DAY.
THE WATER IN THE RIVER FLOWS TOWARDS THE SEA.
THE CHEF COOKED A DELICIOUS MEAL FOR THE GUESTS.
THE BASKETBALL TEAM WON THE CHAMPIONSHIP GAME.
THE DOCTOR CHECKED MY HEARTBEAT AND BLOOD PRESSURE.
THE FLOWERS IN THE GARDEN WERE IN FULL BLOOM.
THE AIRPLANE FLEW HIGH IN THE SKY.
THE MUSIC WAS LOUD AND ENERGETIC AT THE PARTY.
THE POLITICIAN GAVE A SPEECH TO THE CROWD.
THE COMPUTER SCREEN DISPLAYED COLORFUL IMAGES.
THE SNOW FELL SOFTLY ON THE GROUND.
THE BOOKSHELF WAS FILLED WITH BOOKS OF DIFFERENT GENRES.
THE SOCCER BALL ROLLED ACROSS THE FIELD.
THE BABY CRIED WHEN HE WAS HUNGRY.
THE MOON WAS FULL AND BRIGHT IN THE NIGHT SKY.
